      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 21.3 - 老子 21.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 21.3 - 老子 21.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>道之為物，惟恍惟惚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Who can of Dao the nature tell? Our sight it flies, our touch as well.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
