      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 21.18 - 老子 21.19</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>吾何以知眾甫之狀哉？以此。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How know I that it is so with all the beauties of existing things? By this (nature of the Dao).</seg>
      </tuv>
